data.description: Wonderful waterfront community! Spacious town home with hurricane curtain shutters, 2 Bedroom/2 Bathroom offering a private enclosed courtyard with a putting green along one side of the patio, a storage shed, HVAC has UV light, the deck has an undercover to catch the rain, great for entertaining.  Community has a fishing dock, 2 pools, clubhouse, and just a short walk/stroll to the beach. Banana Bay residents have their own personal gate to access convenient shopping and restaurants such as Publix, Florida Fresh Grill, UPS and much more.
